<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.1.3">
<l>kummā yattoṭu veṇṇey viḻuṅkik kuṭattayir cāyttup paruki</l>
<l>poymmā yamaru tāṉa vacuraraip poṉṟuvit tiṉṟunī vantāy</l>
<l>immā yamvalla piḷḷainam pīyuṉṉai yeṉmaka ṉēyeṉpar niṉṟār</l>
<l>ammā vuṉṉai yaṟintukoṇ ṭēṉuṉak kañcuva ṉammam taravē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Devouring the butter along with the well-cooked dahl,</l>
<l rend="indent">tipping over and drinking the curd in pots,</l>
<l>Now you come [along] killing the demon who became</l>
<l rend="indent">a Marutu tree through deception and illusion,</l>
<l>[my] boy prince skilled in illusion!</l>
<l>There are those who stand [here] saying you are my son.</l>
<l>Alas! I have come to know you,</l>
<l rend="indent"> [and] I am afraid to give you [my] breast milk.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
